..TEXT:
|Vespero~ is the last of the four divisions of
the day, from 3 to 6 P.M. (^cf. Conv.~ iii. 6: 20; iv. 23: 129).
When it is 3 P.M. in Italy it is 6 P.M. at Jerusalem and 6 A.M.
in Purgatory (see diagrams on pp. 34 and 35).
